text: Used to be pretty good. Lately been pretty poor quality. Usually just the wings that aren’t that great, but tonight I ordered a large pepperoni lovers pizza and there was barely any pepperoni on the whole thing. Looked really sloppy. If they didn’t have such good deals a lot of the time they would lose my business completely.
